<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>Views in brief</b></font><P>
<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">April 6, 2007 | Page 10</font><P>

<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><B>VIEWS BELOW:</B><BR>
<A HREF="#Deny">Denying health care to all</A><BR>
<A HREF="#Playing">Playing politics with women's lives</A><BR>
